    Class Description
    BadVehicleInformationExceptionTest
    Tests the custom BadVehicleInformationException

    Concrete class representing a hybrid/electric vehicle that can be serviced in HybridElectricBays.

    Test the HybridElectricCar class
    RegularCar
    Concrete class representing a standard vehicle that cannot be serviced in HybridElectricBays.

    Vehicle
    Abstract class representing a vehicle that is serviceable in the garage.

    Tests the VehicleList class
    VehicleTest
    Tests the Vehicle class.

    BadVehicleInformationException
